1
00:00:06,140 --> 00:00:08,540
=Fireworks=

2
00:00:08,540 --> 00:00:10,860
=Episode 18=

3
00:00:11,480 --> 00:00:13,119
You useless fool!

4
00:00:13,800 --> 00:00:15,240
Get lost!

5
00:00:15,887 --> 00:00:16,766
(Zechen.)

6
00:00:21,039 --> 00:00:25,079
Don't come to me impulsively
because of empathic resonance.

7
00:00:25,679 --> 00:00:26,480
Do you hear me?

8
00:00:28,679 --> 00:00:30,320
You've really grown bold!

9
00:00:31,199 --> 00:00:32,479
You even dared to hide

10
00:00:32,479 --> 00:00:34,359
the fact that Qiao Qibang is still alive.

11
00:00:38,960 --> 00:00:40,880
I only just found out myself.

12
00:00:41,287 --> 00:00:44,847
The butler by Qiao Qibang's
side deceived everyone.

13
00:00:52,840 --> 00:00:55,079
If you dare deceive me,

14
00:00:56,159 --> 00:00:58,640
I can't guarantee the safety

15
00:00:59,520 --> 00:01:02,079
of Zemu or Qiao Nian.

16
00:01:02,600 --> 00:01:03,520
Rest assured.

17
00:01:05,439 --> 00:01:06,640
If I intended to deceive you,

18
00:01:06,640 --> 00:01:07,879
I wouldn't have come back.

19
00:01:12,840 --> 00:01:14,599
Right now, Qiao Qibang is unconscious.

20
00:01:15,519 --> 00:01:17,239
He poses no threat to us.

21
00:01:18,040 --> 00:01:20,190
The person in control
of the group is still Qiao Nian.

22
00:01:20,439 --> 00:01:22,319
You're openly opposing her.

23
00:01:22,319 --> 00:01:24,879
I have no way to help you
stop her from raising funds.

24
00:01:27,439 --> 00:01:31,280
But your deep feelings for Qiao Nian,

25
00:01:31,959 --> 00:01:33,400
how am I supposed to trust you?

26
00:01:34,239 --> 00:01:36,239
Isn't Zemu still in your hands?

27
00:01:37,879 --> 00:01:39,400
He is my only family.

28
00:01:40,640 --> 00:01:41,519
Besides,

29
00:01:43,599 --> 00:01:45,280
I've worked for you for so long.

30
00:01:45,280 --> 00:01:47,879
Shouldn't you at least let me see him?

31
00:01:50,537 --> 00:01:51,336
Oh?

32
00:01:58,650 --> 00:01:59,450
Mhm.

33
00:02:02,159 --> 00:02:03,760
Hi, Zechen.

34
00:02:04,319 --> 00:02:05,280
Have you missed me?

35
00:02:05,799 --> 00:02:07,079
Have you been eating well?

36
00:02:07,640 --> 00:02:09,159
Have you been listening to Dad?

37
00:02:09,680 --> 00:02:11,039
Once I finish this busy period,

38
00:02:11,039 --> 00:02:12,680
I'll come back and spend time with you,

39
00:02:12,919 --> 00:02:13,560
alright?

40
00:02:14,120 --> 00:02:15,479
Be good.

41
00:02:15,599 --> 00:02:17,240
Goodbye, I have to get back to work.

42
00:02:19,960 --> 00:02:20,800
(Zemu.)

43
00:02:21,520 --> 00:02:24,360
(Trying to outplay me, are you?)

44
00:02:24,879 --> 00:02:27,599
(We've been searching
for Zemu all these years)

45
00:02:27,599 --> 00:02:28,680
(and found nothing.)

46
00:02:29,520 --> 00:02:31,560
(It's as if he vanished
from the face of the earth.)

47
00:02:32,150 --> 00:02:35,909
(Are you certain he's still alive?)

48
00:02:41,840 --> 00:02:42,599
Nian.

49
00:02:42,599 --> 00:02:43,400
Hey, Mr. Zhou.

50
00:02:43,400 --> 00:02:44,520
I will help you with this matter.

51
00:02:44,520 --> 00:02:45,479
Alright.

52
00:02:45,479 --> 00:02:46,240
Thank you.

53
00:02:46,240 --> 00:02:47,680
Don't worry, it's fine.

54
00:02:54,439 --> 00:02:55,400
You're back.

55
00:02:57,039 --> 00:02:57,919
Are you alright?

56
00:02:57,960 --> 00:02:59,680
I sensed that he was hurting you again.

57
00:03:00,599 --> 00:03:01,400
I'm fine.

58
00:03:01,960 --> 00:03:02,759
What about you?

59
00:03:04,520 --> 00:03:05,400
Does it hurt?

60
00:03:08,120 --> 00:03:10,639
I won't let Jiang Xiao
get away with this.

61
00:03:11,199 --> 00:03:11,759
Wait here,

62
00:03:11,759 --> 00:03:12,560
I'll get an ice pack.

63
00:03:12,960 --> 00:03:13,759
Mhm.

64
00:03:19,800 --> 00:03:21,400
Although I suffered some minor injuries,

65
00:03:22,240 --> 00:03:24,960
at least now we know Jiang
Xiao is targeting the group.

66
00:03:25,759 --> 00:03:26,560
Mhm.

67
00:03:28,800 --> 00:03:29,599
How is it?

68
00:03:30,639 --> 00:03:32,800
Is the fundraising going smoothly?

69
00:03:33,840 --> 00:03:34,879
Fairly well, I suppose.

70
00:03:35,240 --> 00:03:36,400
Quite a number of people

71
00:03:36,400 --> 00:03:37,919
are willing to lend their support

72
00:03:37,919 --> 00:03:38,960
out of respect for Grandpa.

73
00:03:39,520 --> 00:03:41,840
After all, Qiao Group
is such a large enterprise.

74
00:03:42,199 --> 00:03:43,879
If anything were to go wrong,

75
00:03:44,120 --> 00:03:45,400
their partners wouldn't want

76
00:03:45,400 --> 00:03:46,680
to see that happen either.

77
00:03:50,919 --> 00:03:51,719
Is there...

78
00:03:52,719 --> 00:03:54,639
anything I can do to help?

79
00:03:56,240 --> 00:03:57,759
You've done more than enough.

80
00:03:58,319 --> 00:04:00,280
I can handle this matter on my own.

81
00:04:00,600 --> 00:04:02,960
After all, I'm currently largest
shareholder of the company.

82
00:04:03,400 --> 00:04:05,560
There shouldn't be many

83
00:04:05,599 --> 00:04:08,719
who would dare oppose me openly.

84
00:04:10,479 --> 00:04:11,960
Don't worry.

85
00:04:14,000 --> 00:04:15,120
I'll get back to work, then.

86
00:04:15,599 --> 00:04:16,399
Alright.

87
00:04:32,037 --> 00:04:37,462
(Qiao Group Funds)

88
00:04:38,312 --> 00:04:39,112
(Calmness Heals All)

89
00:04:39,112 --> 00:04:39,750
(Qiao Group Funds)

90
00:04:47,462 --> 00:04:50,475
(Dad. Received.)

91
00:04:55,839 --> 00:04:57,000
Hello, Mr. Xu.

92
00:04:57,079 --> 00:04:57,800
Nian.

93
00:04:57,800 --> 00:04:58,600
Mhm.

94
00:04:58,759 --> 00:05:01,240
Recently, my company
has been facing difficulties.

95
00:05:01,250 --> 00:05:03,000
I'm afraid I won't
be able to help this time.

96
00:05:03,000 --> 00:05:03,800
Ah...

97
00:05:04,319 --> 00:05:05,160
I understand.

98
00:05:05,160 --> 00:05:06,160
I'm truly sorry.

99
00:05:18,519 --> 00:05:19,319
It's alright.

100
00:05:19,500 --> 00:05:20,401
There's one month left.

101
00:05:21,000 --> 00:05:22,680
Things will surely improve.

102
00:05:32,480 --> 00:05:36,000
I've told you the entirety
of Qiao Nian's fundraising plan.

103
00:05:36,800 --> 00:05:38,600
When will you let me see Zemu?

104
00:05:40,800 --> 00:05:41,759
No need to rush.

105
00:05:42,639 --> 00:05:45,000
Wait until Qiao Nian
is completely cornered.

106
00:05:47,879 --> 00:05:50,279
This is a fine wine
I've kept for 15 years.

107
00:05:50,839 --> 00:05:52,519
Won't you have a taste?

108
00:05:57,120 --> 00:05:57,920
Qiao Nian?

109
00:05:59,279 --> 00:06:00,120
Why are you here?

110
00:06:00,399 --> 00:06:01,160
Ah?

111
00:06:02,637 --> 00:06:04,720
Nian, let's talk this through calmly.

112
00:06:04,720 --> 00:06:05,680
Calmly?

113
00:06:06,879 --> 00:06:09,600
So you've been deceiving me all along?

114
00:06:09,839 --> 00:06:10,639
Ah?

115
00:06:11,399 --> 00:06:12,720
You heard everything?

116
00:06:13,800 --> 00:06:16,560
I was wondering why
my efforts kept failing.

117
00:06:17,040 --> 00:06:18,319
So it was you sabotaging me.

118
00:06:20,319 --> 00:06:21,519
I trusted you so completely,

119
00:06:21,639 --> 00:06:23,600
yet you've betrayed me again and again.

120
00:06:23,600 --> 00:06:24,959
This is for your own good.

121
00:06:25,120 --> 00:06:26,199
For my own good?

122
00:06:27,800 --> 00:06:31,720
Qiao Group's stock has plunged
due to Qiao Wenjun.

123
00:06:32,319 --> 00:06:33,519
Even if you secure the funds

124
00:06:33,519 --> 00:06:34,600
and pay the penalty,

125
00:06:34,600 --> 00:06:37,360
the company will never
regain its former vitality.

126
00:06:38,399 --> 00:06:41,240
You might as well hand
the Qiao Group over to Dad.

127
00:06:42,160 --> 00:06:44,199
Powerful alliance between Jiang
and Qiao families.

128
00:06:45,439 --> 00:06:46,720
Dad has agreed

129
00:06:47,519 --> 00:06:49,160
to let you remain as chairperson.

130
00:06:50,525 --> 00:06:51,925
Do you hear yourself?

131
00:06:52,240 --> 00:06:53,399
Nian!

132
00:06:53,480 --> 00:06:55,279
- You fool!
- Listen to me, Nian!

133
00:06:55,319 --> 00:06:57,560
What Zechen said is not without reason.

134
00:06:58,160 --> 00:06:58,959
Think about it.

135
00:06:59,000 --> 00:07:01,439
You hand the Qiao Group over to me,

136
00:07:01,519 --> 00:07:03,319
but you still remain the chairperson.

137
00:07:03,399 --> 00:07:05,680
That way, the company won't go bankrupt.

138
00:07:06,000 --> 00:07:08,279
And with the five billion you've raised,

139
00:07:08,360 --> 00:07:09,720
we can expand production.

140
00:07:09,800 --> 00:07:10,959
It's a win-win situation,

141
00:07:11,279 --> 00:07:12,120
don't you think?

142
00:07:14,399 --> 00:07:15,639
The two of you

143
00:07:16,399 --> 00:07:18,120
truly disgust me.

144
00:07:19,199 --> 00:07:20,439
Don't let me see you again.

145
00:07:21,300 --> 00:07:23,019
Don't be so ungrateful.

146
00:07:26,319 --> 00:07:27,720
What were you doing?

147
00:07:28,560 --> 00:07:30,519
You didn't even realize
you were being followed?

148
00:07:33,079 --> 00:07:35,040
No matter what it takes,

149
00:07:35,519 --> 00:07:37,920
before the contract deadline,

150
00:07:37,920 --> 00:07:39,959
you must keep her under control.

151
00:07:41,639 --> 00:07:44,959
(That fool! I should have
signed divorce agreement.)

152
00:07:45,360 --> 00:07:46,330
(Stay far away from him,)

153
00:07:46,639 --> 00:07:47,959
(so he wouldn't keep interfering.)

154
00:07:55,250 --> 00:07:56,087
(Female Party Signature: Qiao Nian)

155
00:07:56,125 --> 00:07:56,975
(Divorce Agreement)

156
00:08:05,879 --> 00:08:06,879
(Song Che calling)
(Song Che?)

157
00:08:10,720 --> 00:08:12,839
Qiao Nian, do you have time to talk?

158
00:08:18,160 --> 00:08:24,130
♪So many words unsaid,
the deeper we fall, the more we fear♪

159
00:08:24,410 --> 00:08:32,010
♪Fate like a gamble,
locking us inside its game♪

160
00:08:32,060 --> 00:08:35,850
♪Hearts at play, truth and lies,
who could ever know♪

161
00:08:36,370 --> 00:08:39,650
♪Where this ends♪

162
00:08:39,650 --> 00:08:46,930
♪I try to walk away,
yet still step into the fire♪

163
00:08:46,930 --> 00:08:51,260
♪Your heartbeat pulls me under,
and I lose myself♪

164
00:08:51,300 --> 00:08:54,380
♪Love turns into pain♪

165
00:08:54,450 --> 00:08:58,570
♪Words betray us
until our eyes burn red♪

166
00:08:58,730 --> 00:09:02,210
♪Yet I still want you close♪

167
00:09:02,210 --> 00:09:06,380
♪Your tide breaks me,
and I fall for you again♪

168
00:09:06,380 --> 00:09:09,690
♪Even if love becomes nothing♪

169
00:09:09,690 --> 00:09:14,260
♪When love and hate fade
into the crowd and the ice melts♪

170
00:09:14,260 --> 00:09:20,570
♪Does it mean we could meet again?♪

171
00:09:21,160 --> 00:09:25,350
♪Your heartbeat pulls me under,
and I lose myself♪

172
